{"tid":2157191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國外長：歐盟將制裁鎮壓示威白俄官員","createTime":"2020-08-15T01:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T10:35:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2de1cb6c35ef49d9a6824c008991fd62cf6901a8","tid":2157191,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:11:50.000Z","msg":"白俄羅斯總統盧卡申科（ Aleksander Lukashenko）高票第六度當選後，觸發民眾連日上街示威，數千人被捕，有示威者投訴被虐打。德國外長馬斯（Heiko Maas）表示，歐盟將向要為鎮壓示威負責的白俄羅斯官員實施新制裁。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯說，過去幾天在白俄羅斯發生的事情完全不能接受，呼籲歐盟作出清晰回應，把參與針對和平示威者犯下罪行的人，置於歐盟的制裁制度，至少6個成員國大致支持制裁，但匈牙利則有疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟27國外長召開緊急視像會議。一名歐盟外交官透露，會議決定，指示歐盟外交政策部門擬備一張個人黑名單，為制裁踏出第一步。<br />\n<br />\n白俄羅斯政府早前向遭受暴力對待的人致歉，於周五釋放多名被捕人士。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2725485</code></pre>"},{"pid":"d042038cf0ef476ea6c9dfd388fe0078398085ba","tid":2157191,"uid":270506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:35:53.000Z","msg":"咁幾時輪到香港呢？"},{"pid":"d2eebe9b069fbb38e39fbf7fef44f92643b24f9e","tid":2157191,"uid":10503,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d042038cf0ef476ea6c9dfd388fe0078398085ba","tid":2157191,"uid":270506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:35:53.000Z","msg":"咁幾時輪到香港呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:39:19.000Z","msg":"人民幣 真香"},{"pid":"4bb87564df9afae05548386e7b1fcb290972e6c4","tid":2157191,"uid":202466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:40:24.000Z","msg":"幾快手"},{"pid":"5172377a07f150fc97996afa656b4b41493426af","tid":2157191,"uid":158755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2eebe9b069fbb38e39fbf7fef44f92643b24f9e","tid":2157191,"uid":10503,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d042038cf0ef476ea6c9dfd388fe0078398085ba","tid":2157191,"uid":270506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:35:53.000Z","msg":"咁幾時輪到香港呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:39:19.000Z","msg":"人民幣 真香"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:43:46.000Z","msg":"呢啲小國對於歐盟本身係負擔<br />\n點同祖國比呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c855e6c0abcd46ab170c5d4f48a5b04df6834bc","tid":2157191,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610f6cb848b63ec58ad05419b1e861863eba7e96","tid":2157191,"uid":300644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:51:30.000Z","msg":"迅速行動"},{"pid":"9418ca154a46931751a9f156d7f16f4ffaa1cf57","tid":2157191,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:08:06.000Z","msg":"同中國冇關就立即做野<br />\n德國&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"2160515336d29baae11aa7103649f15ed9d33a50","tid":2157191,"uid":127176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T10:35:21.000Z","msg":"未做嘢果陣就屌人偽善對暴行視而不見<br />\n到人地做嘢果陣就嫌厚此薄彼<br />\n連登仔究竟想人點，明明係一件值得支持嘅事，見係歐盟做就搵位屌"}]}